					<div class="commentheading">On December 21, 2007 at 06:32 PM, JoeinPhila said...</div>
					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>Carry Over?</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody">So when you pull the roast with an internal temp of 140-145, it is still very red? Can you describe the redness a bit better? all of the charts Ive seen would put a 145 degree roast firmly in the medium zone.<br />
