					<div class="commentheading">On November 22, 2008 at 10:14 PM, mschweitzer (guest) said...</div>
					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>prime rib</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody">Hi there,<br />
<br />
I've never cooked a prime rib before.  I'm doing an 11 lb. roast for Thanksgiving.  There's no mention of whether to cover the roast or not--what is your preference?  Also, at 200 degrees x 11 lbs. I will be cooking the roast for 8 hrs????  Can that be right?  Thanks for the help!</div>
