					<div class="commentheading">On April 04, 2010 at 03:43 PM, uzart (guest) said...</div>
					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>Stones</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody">...Cook a roast weighting 1 stone for 45 mins/lbs at 122C .......<br />
<br />
